-- Koutons Retail Gains 10% in Mumbai After Saying Debt at Manageable Limits
-- B y   P a r e s h   J a t a k i a
-- 2010-10-04T04:01:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/koutons-retail-gains-10-in-mumbai-after-saying-debt-at-manageable-limits.html
Koutons Retail India Ltd. rose in
Mumbai trading after saying its debt is “within manageable
limits.”  The shares climbed as much as 10.1 percent and changed
hands at 169.95 rupees at 9:29 a.m. local time. About 5.9
percent of its equity, or 1.8 million shares, changed hands in
nine block deals today, data on the Bloomberg showed.  To contact the reporter on this story:
